transcript:
Hello.
Executive: Haan hello, haan ji madam aap se video meeting ke liye baat hui thi na?
Customer: Ji ji bataiye.
Executive: Haan to free hai aap?
Customer: Ji main free hoon.
Executive: Kya to aap mujhe mail id de do. 
Executive: Koi jo aapne login kar rakhi hai koi bhi.
Customer: Ah main abhi bhejti hoon. Abhi isi call pe doon ya main aapko message kar sakti hoon?
Executive: Aap mujhe call kar lo, aap mujhe call kar lo.
Customer: Theek hai, main abhi call karti hoon aapko.
Executive: Theek, theek, okay.
Customer: Okay, okay, theek hai.
